# Enclaves

## List all enclaves

```shell
curl "<%= config[:api_url] %>/enclaves/"
```

This endpoint lists all enclaves.

### HTTPS Request

`GET <%= config[:api_url] %>/enclaves/`

## Create a new enclave

```shell
curl "<%= config[:api_url] %>/enclaves/" \
-X POST
```

This endpoint creates a new enclave.

### HTTPS Request

`POST <%= config[:api_url] %>/enclaves/`


## List a specific enclave

```shell
curl "<%= config[:api_url] %>/enclave/2"
```

This endpoint lists an enclave by its enclaveID.

### HTTPS Request

`GET <%= config[:api_url] %>/enclave/<enclaveID>`


### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
enclaveID | The ID of the enclave to retrieve

## Delete a specific Enclave

```shell
curl "<%= config[:api_url] %>/enclave/2" \
  -X DELETE
```

This endpoint deletes a specific Enclave.

### HTTPS Request

`DELETE <%= config[:api_url] %>/enclave/<enclaveID>`

### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
enclaveID | The ID of the enclave to delete

## Shows enclave stats by enclaveID

```shell
curl "<%= config[:api_url] %>/enclave/2/stats"
```

This endpoint show enclave stats by its enclaveID.

### HTTPS Request

`GET <%= config[:api_url] %>/enclave/<enclaveID/stats>`


### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
enclaveID | The ID of the enclave to retrieve
